3 JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 12. As used in this chapter, "land use and zoning
4 plan" means the land use and zoning overlay district plan adopted by
5 the eligible county with the formation of the district.
6 SECTION 2. IC 36-10-16-17, AS ADDED BY P.L.141-2025,
7 SECTION 1, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
8 JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 17. (a) The commission may be established by the
9 legislative body of an eligible:
10 (1) county; and
11 (2) city;
12 upon the adoption of an ordinance approved by both bodies
13 establishing the commission.
14 (b) The ordinance establishing the commission shall designate the
15 boundaries of the Midwest continental divide district, if the legislative
16 bodies determine the following:
17 (1) The district's designation would encourage collaboration and
